name: Sfenj Simulator
description:
Define the game? Sfenj Simulator is a 3D Moroccan game, the player is on a cardboard bag, and the player is trying to collect sfenj, which by the way is Moroccan food. We do not want to talk about a game a lot, and in order not to spoil the stages of the game, we will make you discover a game for yourself. Follow us :
